1. *Glumica* je sinoć bila izvanredna u predstavi. (The actress was outstanding in the play last night.)
2. Nisam siguran da li je *glumica* bila zadovoljna svojom ulogom. (I'm not sure if the actress was satisfied with her role.)
3. Sve *glumice* u ovoj produkciji su vrlo talentovane. (All the actresses in this production are very talented.)
4. Jutros sam sreo poznatu *glumicu* u parku. (I met a famous actress in the park this morning.)
5. Zanimljivo je kako se uloge u pozorištu dodeljuju *glumicama* i glumcima. (It's interesting how roles in theater are assigned to actresses and actors.)
6. *Glumicu* su pred kraj filma zamenili drugom glumicom. (They replaced the actress with another actress towards the end of the movie.)
7. Ova *glumica* igra glavnu ulogu u novom filmu. (This actress plays the lead role in the new movie.)
8. Da li si čuo za novu *glumicu* koja je postala popularna na TikToku? (Have you heard of the new actress who became popular on TikTok?)
9. Našao sam posao kao *glumičin* pomoćnik na snimanju filma. (I got a job as the actress's assistant on the movie set.)
10. *Glumica* je proslavila rođendan sa svojom porodicom. (The actress celebrated her birthday with her family.)